m for measuring and reducing emissions of greenhouse gases from its suppliers and scoring maximum points for its thorough paper procurement policy in the november  report hp was ranked second with a score of  hp does especially well for its disclosure of externally verified greenhouse gas emissions and its setting of targets for reducing themthirdparty source needed however greenpeace reports that hp risks a penalty point in future editions due to the fact that it is a member of trade associations that have commented against energy efficiency standards hp has earned recognition of its work in the area of data privacy and security in  the company ranked no  in the ponemon institutes annual study of the most trusted companies for privacy since  hp has worked directly with the us congress the federal trade commission ftc and the department of commerce to establish a new strategy for federal legislation hp played a key role in work toward the december  ftc report protecting consumer privacy in an era of rapid change after winning nine straight annual most respected company in china awards from the economic observer and peking university hp china has added the  year contribution award to its list of accolades the award aims to identify companies doing business in china with outstanding and sustained performance in business operations development and corporate social responsibility in its  rankings of consumer electronics companies on progress relating to conflict minerals the enough project rated hp second out of  companies calling it a pioneer of progress brandedit a hewlettpackard sponsored porsche  gt cup the company sponsored the hp pavilion at san jose now sap center at san jose home to the nhls san jose sharks according to a businessweek study hp was the worlds th most valuable brand as of  hp has many sponsorships one well known sponsorship is mission space in epcot at the walt disney world resort from  to  and again from  hp has been the shirt sponsor of premier 