he case study watch the video abb drives better outcomes using iot abb one of the largest industrial automation solution providers harnesses the power of iot to drive efficiency for better outcomes with less resource investment watch the video hirotec cuts time to manually inspect by  hirotec’s new infrastructure eliminates data processing latency and provides analysis in real time to help it efficiently manage its factory machinery read the case study rio upgrades its airport technology riogaleão airport upgraded its infrastructure to accommodate a doubling of its visitors during the olympics watch the video creating connected digitized race cars an automobile race team gets valuable location traffic and conditions data helping it set a world record by driving  kilometers from south africa to norway in nine days watch the video kaeser cuts downtime by  kaeser kompressoren delivers realtime analytics that predict and prevent outages before they occur gaining a competitive advantage by enhancing customer care and satisfaction read the case study japanese university reduces congestion kyushu university analyzes traffic patterns in fukuoka japan to optimize signaling and routing and improve the quality of life read the case study iot in action   of  accelerating iot insights with hpe and deloitte as the technology landscape evolves networks must provide context and actionable insights from the core to the edge see how aruba can help you reach the intelligent edge hpe and deloitte have developed a series of offerings and services to help businesses develop longterm secure iot solutions to help drive revenue growth cost savings and operational efficiencies read more read less   of  hpe and ge digital partner to empower the intelligent edge by combining hpe’s hybrid it capabilities and broad services footprint with ge’s predix a paas solution for the industrial internet this partnership is transforming iiot insights into action read more read less   of  texmark and hpe implement the refinery of the future texmark and hpe implement the refinery of the future read more read less  accelerating iot insights with hpe and deloitte  hpe and ge digital partner to empower the intelligent edge  texmark and hpe implement the refinery of the future previous next elements of an iot solution connectivity iot connectivity represents great potential it can automate decisions and be a catalyst for new products and services but only when insights come from data collected through secure connections and trusted devices iot can enable new business models and revenue streams by monetizing device data through a scalable modular ubiquitous iot platform that offers device and service management on premise or through the cloud connect and protect your iot with hpe aruba solutions hpe universal iot platform esg white paper iot connectivity compute data flows from things to collection analysis and storage insights derived from data analytics can be required in real time for immediate response or can be aggregated for later use for realtime insights data processing should occur at its source computing at the edge reduces delay and avoids bandwidth consumption while transmitting data to the cloud or data center get the right amount of compute at the right place—whether at the edge for immediate insight in the cloud or data center—to efficiently power your iot deployment esg white paper iot compute hpe edgeline iot systems security the vast volumes of device data in the iot must be protected from theft modification and exploitation from the instant it is created security has to continue while data is in transit through the network at rest in data stores and when in use by applications leverage effective countermeasures—proactively end to end hpe security solutions top  security problems with iot devices secure your apps with hpe fortify connect and protect your iot devices datadriven insights iot technology produces data in volumes and levels of diversity that challenge traditional approaches to storage and processing as a result data scientists and developers are collaborating on new ways of extracting business insights hidden in huge troves of device data you then benefit by seeing your iot insights turn into business efficiencies new customers and new revenue streams become a datadriven organization with iot partner ecosystem iot solutions need to tap into multiple technologies iot requires an ecosystem of companies enabled by education tools and support our vast network of partners is at your disposal to help you address constantlyevolving requirements and stakeholders the hpe edgeline innovation network accelerates the development of thirdparty edgeline offerings learn about hpe partner programs explore the hpe  ge digital alliance join the edgeline innovation network services no matter where you are in your iot journey you can benefit from an experienced services partner to help navigate the landscape of sensors gateways connectivity compute analytics and business processes we can help assess your current environment and financial model design your architecture and implement your iot based on business needs and industry parameters learn about hpe iot service offerings iot at work see how iot enables new business models and generates industry innovation control the energy grid endtoend leverage advanced smart metering solutions to serve the fastgrowing energy utility marketplace maximize efficiencies to meet your most demanding data acquisition and management challenges today and into the future read the paper save money and power with lighting efficiency cities can optimize energy consumption by remotely managing individual lights monitoring enables preventative and reactive maintenance reducing outages and lowering operating costs read the paper the iot creates connected cars the car of the future will have advanced diagnostics connected media payasyougo insurance realtime service and more cars are becoming selfaware